Execution-Correlation Command
  --prefetch-dir <path>  Prefetch directory
  --jumplist-path <path> Jump List source file or directory
  --shortcuts-base <path> Base user directory for shortcut scan
  --limit <N>            Limit rows (default: 200, max: 5000)
  --json                 Print data payload JSON to stdout
  --json-result <file>   Write envelope JSON to file
  --quiet                Suppress console summary output
